{"lemma":"مَطْبَخَيْ","slug":"مَطْبَخَيْ","root":"ط.ب.خ","root_slug":"ط-ب-خ","root_link":"/words/roots/ط-ب-خ","pos":"N","pos_camel":"noun","paradigm":[],"frequency_in_corpus":0,"cross_references":{"qac":{"found":false},"wiktextract":{"found":true,"entry_count":1,"pos_tags":["noun"],"has_etymology":true,"sense_count":2},"lanes":{"found":true,"entry_ids":["n26306","n26307","n26308","n26310"],"search_url":"https://lanelexicon.com/?s=%D9%85%D9%8E%D8%B7%D9%92%D8%A8%D9%8E%D8%AE%D9%8E%D9%8A%D9%92"}},"translations":null,"definition":{"source":"wiktextract","senses":[{"pos":"noun","gloss":"kitchen"},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"cuisine, style of cooking"}]},"etymology":{"source":"wiktextract","text":"Noun of place from the verb طَبَخَ (ṭabaḵa), from the root ط ب خ (ṭ b ḵ). Compare with Hebrew מִטְבָּח (miṭbaḥ /⁠mitbákh⁠/)"},"ipa":["/matˤ.bax/"],"lanes_definition":{"source":"lanes","entries":[{"entry_id":"n26306","headword_ar":"مَطْبَخٌ","root":"Tbx","body":[{"kind":"text","text":"(S, Mgh, Msb, K) and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"miTobaxN","text_ar":"مِطْبَخٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":", (Mgh, Msb,) sometimes called by the latter name as being likened to an instrument, (Msb,) and this latter is the only form mentioned in the A, and is said by Sb to be not a noun of place, but a subst. like"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"mirobadN","text_ar":"مِرْبَدٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (TA,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A place of cooking; a place in which cooking is performed;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, A, Mgh, Msb, K;)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a cook's house"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"room; a kitchen."},{"kind":"text","text":"(T.) [See also"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"muT~abaxN","text_ar":"مُطَّبَخٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":".] One says,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"huwa A^aboyaDu AlmaTobaxi","text_ar":"هُوَ اَبْيَضُ المَطْبَخِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(tropical:)  [lit."},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He is one whose kitchen,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"cooking-place, is white;"},{"kind":"text","text":"meaning"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"he is inhospitable;"},{"kind":"text","text":"like as one says in the contrary case,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"huwa kaviyru Alr~amaAdi","text_ar":"هُوَ كَثِيرُ الرَّمَادِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"]: and in like manner,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"humo biyDu AlmaTaAbixi","text_ar":"هُمْ بِيضُ المَطَابِخِ"},{"kind":"text","text":". (A.)"}],"source_refs":["S","Mgh","Msb","K","TA"]},{"entry_id":"n26307","headword_ar":"مِطْبَخٌ","root":"Tbx","body":[{"kind":"italic_en","text":"An implement for cooking:"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a cooking-pot."},{"kind":"text","text":"(K.) ―         -b2-  See also the next preceding paragraph."}],"source_refs":[]},{"entry_id":"n26308","headword_ar":"مُطَبِّخُ","root":"Tbx","body":[{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A young"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"lizard of the species called"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Dab~","text_ar":"ضَبّ"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"in a certain stage of its growth"},{"kind":"text","text":"]: in its first stage it is called"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"HisolN","text_ar":"حِسْلٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"; then,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"gayodaAqN","text_ar":"غَيْدَاقٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"; then,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"muTab~ixN","text_ar":"مُطَبِّخٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"; then,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xuDarimN","text_ar":"خُضَرِمٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"; and then,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Dab~N","text_ar":"ضَبٌّ"},{"kind":"text","text":": (S, L:) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"one that has nearly attained to the size of its parent:"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"one in its fullest state:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(ISd, L:) or the"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"first of the offspring of the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Dab~","text_ar":"ضَبّ"},{"kind":"text","text":"("},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^aw~alu waladi","text_ar":"اَوَّلُ وَلَدِ"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AlD~ab~i","text_ar":"الضَّبِّ"},{"kind":"text","text":"). (K. [But this is evidently a mistake, as is observed in the TK.]) ―         -b2-  And"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A young man that is full"},{"kind":"text","text":"[or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"plump"},{"kind":"text","text":"]: (K:) a child when born is called"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"raDiyEN","text_ar":"رَضِيعٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"TifolN","text_ar":"طِفْلٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"; then"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"faTiymN","text_ar":"فَطِيمٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"; then,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"daArijN","text_ar":"دَارِجٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"; then,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"jaforN","text_ar":"جَفْرٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"; then,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"yaAfiEN","text_ar":"يَافِعٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"; then"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"$adaxN","text_ar":"شَدَخٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"; then,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"muTab~ixN","text_ar":"مُطَبِّخٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"; and then,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"kawokabN","text_ar":"كَوْكَبٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":". (IAar, TA.)"}],"source_refs":["S","L","ISd","K"]},{"entry_id":"n26310","headword_ar":"مُطَّبَخٌ","root":"Tbx","body":[{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A place in which people cook their food."},{"kind":"text","text":"(JK,) One says,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"h`*aA muT~abaxu Alqawomi wah`*aA mu$otawaAhumo","text_ar":"هٰذَا مُطَّبَخُ القَوْمِ وَهٰذَا مُشْتَوَاهُمْ"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"This is the people's place of cooking their food, and this is the place of their roasting"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"broiling"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"frying"},{"kind":"text","text":"]. (S.) [See also"},{"ki